        "id": 3310274,
        "name": "Jayson Cohen",
        "username": "Jayson_Cohen",
        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/j/8797f3/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2022-01-06T00:15:33.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I don\u2019t know if this explains it, but there was a period of time when Chartron would sell grapes or grant rights to them to other producers.  For ex., I bought a bottle of 1993 Verget Caillerets VV at auction that Jean-Marie Guffens told me was the only year he bottled Caillerets and that it was sourced from Chartron.<br>\n<img src=\"/uploads/db3686/original/3X/f/6/f6662adf6c2f8a8150847ee0e86826789bd97c1a.jpeg\" alt=\"image.jpg\" data-base62-sha1=\"z9KlJqRS1t4vO0v8ahbxmpuFQQW\" width=\"4032\" height=\"3024\"></p>",
