      {
        "id": 3310330,
        "name": "Alex Damario",
        "username": "AlexD",
        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/a/96bed5/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2022-01-06T01:17:24.000Z",
        "cooked": "<aside class=\"quote no-group\" data-post=\"2\" data-topic=\"176047\">\n<blockquote>\n<p>I don\u2019t know if this explains it, but there was a period of time when Chartron would sell grapes or grant rights to them to other producers.  For ex., I bought a bottle of 1993 Verget Caillerets VV at auction that Jean-Marie Guffens told me was the only year he bottled Caillerets and that it was sourced from Chartron.</p>\n</blockquote>\n</aside>\n<p>That would make sense, thank you!</p>",
